column16: Justin Upton grounds into a force out, shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria to second baseman Derek Dietrich.   Andrew Romine out at 2nd.
Nick Castellanos lines out to second baseman Derek Dietrich.
Victor Martinez lines out to shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria.
Miguel Cabrera singles on a ground ball to right fielder Giancarlo Stanton.   Cameron Maybin scores.
Cameron Maybin doubles (4) on a line drive to left fielder Christian Yelich.   Ian Kinsler scores.
Jose Iglesias lines out to left fielder Christian Yelich.
Jarrod Saltalamacchia doubles (5) on a line drive to left fielder Christian Yelich.
Steven Moya flies out to right fielder Giancarlo Stanton.
Justin Upton grounds out, shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria to first baseman Chris Johnson.
